Mijn naam is Gonne-Marieke Kroon-Lamers, trotse eigenaar van Uw Officemanager.NL.

Het bedrijf dat u als ondernemer kan helpen met al uw secretariële, officemanagement, administratieve  en social media werkzaamheden.

Ik bedoel daarmee dat ik als officemanager onder meer de volgende werkzaamheden kan uitvoeren: 
- het notuleren van vergaderingen;
- het verzorgen van mailings;
- het verzorgen van zakelijke correspondentie;
- het corrigeren, redigeren en opmaken van teksten, rapporten, scripties en dergelijke;
- het beheren van (adres)bestanden;
- het uitwerken van geluidsbanden;
- het organiseren van een congres, bijeenkomst of een ander evenement;
- het bijhouden en/of opzetten van uw (financiële) administratie;
- het helpen met uw social media;
- het versturen van nieuwsbrieven;
- het beheren van uw agenda;
- het helpen met uw e-mails.

Wat zijn de voordelen voor u, indien u mij inhuurt: 

- Tijdsbesparing door het uitbesteden van werkzaamheden die niet tot uw specialiteiten behoren. U krijgt meer tijd voor uw corebusiness. Meer tijd om datgene te doen waar u goed in bent;
- Kostenbesparing omdat u géén dure uitzendbureaus, géén extra kantoorruimte en/of meubiliar (indien u wenst, kan ik de werkzaamheden namelijk thuis uitvoeren), géén wervings-en selectie kosten en géén hoge personele kosten hoeft te betalen.

U krijgt een professionele, ervaren, nauwkeurige en toegewijde officemanager. Inzetbaar wanneer u het wenst. En: tegen een concurrerend tarief!

A Secretaria Municipal de Mobilidade Urbana de Belo Horizonte (SMMUR) é responsável por planejar, coordenar, fiscalizar e implementar as políticas públicas de mobilidade da capital.

Criada em 2025, a SMMUR atua de forma integrada com a Sumob e a BHTrans, sendo o órgão central do sistema de mobilidade urbana do município.

Entre suas atribuições estão:

Gestão do trânsito e do transporte público e privado regulamentado;

Planejamento e administração da infraestrutura de mobilidade (terminais, ciclovias, estações etc.);

Implantação e manutenção da sinalização viária;

Coordenação de operações especiais e emergenciais;

Gestão dos fundos municipais de mobilidade.

Com foco em deslocamentos seguros, sustentáveis e eficientes, a SMMUR trabalha para uma cidade mais acessível, conectada e com qualidade de vida para todas as pessoas.

EU-FIRE Kft. was established as a wholly family-owned Hungarian enterprise in 2001. Since then our company has

-	participated as a designer and main contractor in several important property development projects;
-	become a crucial contributor – as an investor and engineering expert in the development of geothermal energy sources – to Hungarian environment-friendly property developments and investments;
-	expanded the range of activities of the corporate group, such that they not only include gene conservation and agricultural R&D projects, but also a pig farm, Hungarian grey cattle breeding and sylviculture;
-	expanded activities also with production, high-tech, and innovative technological projects;
-	run a metal working division, which supplies items to many transport and industrial production companies;
-	created, as a health care industry investor, a substantial Hungarian owned supplier capacity for Hungarian health care; 
-	established high quality family- and environment-friendly places of accommodation across Hungary.

For our exciting projects please visit our web site.

Sekhon Family Office ( SFO ) is a family-operated private office, advancing personal, philanthropic & business endeavors of all generations of the Sekhon Family.

SFO, a dominant force in the Family Office & Private Equity sector with a global presence, plays a pivotal role in shaping the future of international finance.

With a robust financial arsenal, SFO boldly engages in ventures often seen as too risky or unconventional—ranging from restructuring sovereign debt to propelling fiscal growth & spearheading transformative projects across various industries without constraint by location or sector.

We are poised to utilize our extensive network to develop daring financial ventures, offering substantial investments in burgeoning markets, significant capital injections across businesses of all sizes & innovative financial solutions that challenge conventional approaches.

Furthermore, SFO is not merely a financier but a formidable entity in commodities trading & capital market strategies, redefining scope of what a family office can accomplish.

We invite you to join us in this journey into future, where investments transcend mere transactions & become transformative actions that impact the global financial scene.

Explore the vast possibilities within our scope—from real estate investments to high-stakes trading and more. Our commitment extends to bolstering political resolve and pioneering entrepreneurial strategies to drive positive change worldwide.

Our goal is to effect significant, impactful change by fostering extensive relationships that cultivate:
• new-age political leadership;
• new-age governance;
• new-age businesses;
• new-age institutions;
• new-age talent;
• new-age networks;
• new-age enterprises;
• new-age capabilities.

SFO funds & builds the above to tackle challenges and seize opportunities for a better future.

Let's not just meet the future; let's create it.

For us, legacy is not just about what we leave behind; it's about how we live today.

